{"tid":193972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柯P再開砲　批新加坡：住籠子的金絲雀","createTime":"2017-04-09T16:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T17:02:34.000Z","uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ae12cd644a3fd93b13d29938d17151c59efc90","tid":193972,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170409/1094239/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170409%2F1094239%2F&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=05050a54\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170409/1094239/</a><br />\n2017年04月09日17:47      <br />\n（更新：新增配音影片）<br />\n台北市長柯文哲上月26日出訪泰國時，語出驚人說「香港很無聊，就一個小島有什麼好看的」，引發話題。他今出席演講場合時，提及新加坡則形容是「住在籠子的金絲雀」。<br />\n柯文哲今天出席新新聞舉辦的演講時，以日前出訪馬泰印引出台灣的自由、民主、多元價值。柯先形容，他出訪東南亞「才知道他們對台北多羡慕，頻問我2014年是如何選上的」。<br />\n柯文哲說，泰國政變3年多，也沒有選舉，市長還是政府派的；馬國則是因國內有宗教及種族衝突，新加坡就不用說了，「是住在籠子的金絲雀」。印度則有印度教及伊斯蘭教無法融合，而台北的藍綠幾乎被他打破，有一半都被他解決掉，馬來西亞的國會議員都羡慕得流口水，那就是台灣的民主多元已成亞洲的價值。<br />\n語畢，柯文哲一度欲言又止，但他還是忍不住說，攝影機太多無法盡情地說，但他還是要說：「香港不是只有小，連選舉都沒有，有什麼好羡慕；自由的靈魂都沒有，連選舉的自由都沒有」。（郭美瑜／台北報導）"},{"pid":"3d68020c2bb8c3ed4c8e163b08c4ea2091fea988","tid":193972,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"祟台狗: 台灣有民主,台灣no.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86c3059dd160c595c29dcd3550c53de81dacfbe","tid":193972,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:05:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢其實係比共產黨收買左，做臭台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0c818fabb4eec92ea86622297c78dddd66d24a","tid":193972,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf3e57f495cffd5c60221ace57ac0e621fa71bd","tid":193972,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05b0852b62df0c68a1595765f923d4a5ccc2650","tid":193972,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"佢屌晒全部鄰國<br />\n<br />\n典型自大、井底之蛙台狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d67136565655a6710be178fa20bc194d99dec9f","tid":193972,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:35:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37c9cf25091c4d1b024fc513537a06f4a62e70bf","tid":193972,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fb652e94e788850562b622749cb3aa33c1af818","tid":193972,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:44:52.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦 知你台灣係大支那圈度好民主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7db6932bc8e2e59f99fdfd9eb97f084a95b8bf","tid":193972,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台豬如果真係咁好咁發達，就唔洗踩港博泰國生意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜郎國 我諗起呢個國家"},{"pid":"09f1b630f455ee64efc6f145fe152f1fb683e3a2","tid":193972,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"講真話又要比人屌<br />\n做人真係一定要下下都咁撚虛偽 下下淨係話個個國家都好好？<br />\n佢講d野雖然係串 但的確係事實<br />\n香港就算幾繁榮都好 連市民想自己選個特首既權力都無 除左收入高d 文化好d之外 同第三世界獨裁國家有乜春分別"}]}